description: The Solactive ISS ESG Developed Markets Net Zero Pathway Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-capitalisation companies from global developed markets which are selected and weighted with the aim of seeking alignment with EU Paris Aligned Benchmark standards and certain net zero frameworks ESG exclusions Reviewed on a semi-annual basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.solactive.com .
name: Xtrackers World Net Zero Pathway Paris Aligned UCITS ETF 1C
